{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-04310/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-04310"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:43:10"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld, pan, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman walks down a hallway toward a dressing room."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-04310","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-04310"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/canvas/1/3670ffa0-6dff-4b35-a44a-77606df30599","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T19:39:58.346Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The red dresses Alma wears when she meets Reynolds and when they go on their first date are, of course, a far cry from the couture clothes she’ll wear throughout the rest of the film. Nonetheless, their vibrant color, also unlike the muted colors that Reynolds will sometimes dress her in, symbolizes the energy and dynamism that she’ll bring into Reynolds’s life. Costume designer Mark Bridges all but confirms this link between dresses and explains that it was a visual echo requested by PTA himself in an interview with Hunter Harris (“<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW49095816 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.vulture.com/2018/01/the-story-behind-phantom-threads-majestic-couture-dresses.html\"><u>The Story</u></a>”).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1007.8061911170929,293.86271870794087,472.89367429340507,642.1534320323015"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/canvas/1/a0fafc5a-314b-46fc-a312-321962b1edd1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T19:40:13.580Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The camera moves significantly more as it follows Alma than it does for the other models. This calls back to Reynold’s previous complaint that she shouldn’t “move so much.” She does not comply with his request and stands out as much more expressive and fluid than the other models.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-04310/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:83.98384925975776,67.7523553162854,467.7254374158815,306.2180349932706"}}}]}]}]}